org: edudev
app: examen-eduardo
service: starwars-api

provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: nodejs18.x
  region: us-east-2
  stage: dev
  environment:
    NODE_ENV: ${opt:stage, 'dev'}

functions:
  app:
    handler: src/app.handler
    timeout: 29
    events:
      - http:
          path: characters/internal
          method: get
          cors: true
      - http:
          path: characters/internal/{id}
          method: get
          cors: true
      - http:
          path: characters/external
          method: get
          cors: true
      - http:
          path: characters/external/{id}
          method: get
          cors: true
      - http:
          path: planets/internal
          method: get
          cors: true
      - http:
          path: planets/internal/{id}
          method: get
          cors: true
      - http:
          path: planets/external
          method: get
          cors: true
      - http:
          path: planets/external/{id}
          method: get
          cors: true
      - http:
          path: api-docs
          method: get
          cors: true
      - http:
          path: characters/internal
          method: post
          cors: true
      - http:
          path: planets/internal
          method: post
          cors: true
plugins:
  - serverless-offline

custom:
  serverless-offline:
    stage: ${opt:stage, 'dev'}
    port: 3000
